____________________________________________ Difference Array Technique ______________________________________________________
Ekhane jei problem ta niye deal kortesi ta holo ekta array dewa ache jar proti ta index er value 0 diye initialize kora.
Amader ke q songkhok query dibe . Oi q songkhok query te l r x dewa thakbe . Jekhane l theke r porjonto x add korte hobe.
Er jonne amra jei technique ta apply kori take bole difference array technique . Amra shokol l er jonne preCalc[l] += x 
kore dei and preCalc[r+1] -= x kore dei .  Ekhon jodi shompurno array tar prefixSum calculate kori tahole amra jei rokom 
array cheyechilam thik oi rokom ekta array peye jabo . Karon ekhon cumulative sum nile jei jayga porjonto oi x er bistar
houwar kotha chilo thik oi jayga porjonto oi x bistrito hobe . Erporer index e -x hoye jawar karone x er bistar atke jabe.

void IcpcDhakaRegionalist2025(){
    ll n ; cin >> n ; vll vec(n+2,0) ; tamjid(n) cin >> vec[i+1] ;
    ll query ; cin >> query ; 
    while(query-->0){
        ll left , right , value ; cin >> left >> right >> value ;
        vec[left] += value ; vec[right+1] -= value ;
    }
    for(int i = 1 ; i < len(vec) ; i++) vec[i] += vec[i-1] ;
    display(vec) ; cout << sesh ;
}
