                                CSES PROBLEMSET TASK 1661 --->  SubArray Sums II

void IcpcDhakaRegionalist2025(){
    ll n , x ; cin >> n >> x ; ll ans = 0 ; map<ll,ll> mp ;
    vll vec(n) , preSum(n+2,0) ; tamjid(n) cin >> vec[i] ;
    tamjid(n) preSum[i+1] = preSum[i] + vec[i] ;
    for(int i = 0 ; i <= n ; i++){
        if(mp[preSum[i]-x]) ans += mp[preSum[i]-x] ; 
        mp[preSum[i]]++ ;
    }
    cout << ans << sesh ;
}

Ei problem tar sathe previous problem tar ektu vinnota royeche . Ei problem er vector er element gular value negative o hote pare .
Previous problem e chilo shob value >= 1 . Tai oi problem er answer calculation er shomoy amader ke ans er sathe koto add korbo ta
hishab korte hoy ni . Karon ( preSum-target ) er occurance kebol ekbar e houwa shomvob chilo . Kintu ekhon jokhon negative value add
hocche tokhon preSum-target er value previously any number of times occur korte pare . Tai kotobar age occur hoise ta ekta map diye
calculate kore rakha hocche . Ar answer er sathe value ta add kore dewa hocche age jei koybar occur hoise . Karon oi subarray jehetu
jug biyug kore kuno value bartese na tai ager jayga theke eto tukur jugfol hocche 0 . Tar mane age joto tuko ongsho subArraySum = 
target dicchilo oitukur sathe array er ei part ta jug korle oi kuno problem nai .
